     C           KEYQ6     KLIST
     C                     KFLD           K@DTYM  60
     C                     KFLD           A2BHB1
     C                     KFLD           A2BHB2
     C                     KFLD           A2BHB3
     C                     Z-ADDP@DTYM    K@DTYM
